# https://github.com/addityasingh/movie-finder/blob/13e7cdb18e50de6783b4f970375722f7ad63ee0b/src/typedefs/query.graphql:
# import Movie from 'movie.graphql'

type Query {
    Movie(title: String!): Movie
}
# https://github.com/addityasingh/movie-finder/blob/13e7cdb18e50de6783b4f970375722f7ad63ee0b/src/typedefs/movie.graphql:
type Movie {
    id: ID!
    Title: String!
    Actors: String!
    Genre: String!
    Awards: String!
    Country: String!
    Director: String!
    Language: String!
    Metascore: Float!
    Plot: String!
    Poster: String!
    Rated: String!
    Ratings: String!
    Released: Float!
    Response: String!
    Runtime: Float!
    Type: String!
    Writer: String!
    Year: Float!
    imdbID: String!
    imdbRating: Float!
    imdbVotes: Float!
    totalSeasons: Float!
}
